{"tid":827463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新亞assembly田北辰高鐵睇法總結","createTime":"2018-09-19T02:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T03:18:10.000Z","uid":167329,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3283ee729b7f419ec0aee9c0eceb8d6b679a40d1","tid":827463,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"以下係由小弟聽咗兩個鐘既重點<br />\n用手機打 排牌唔好請見諒<br />\n<br />\n1<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 超支係理所當然</span><br />\n田生話其實個個人都知一定會超支<br />\n因為本身政府開出嚟既底價係低過市價好多<br />\n港鐵入紙都會低 到時再要求加<br />\n用處係易通過立法會<br />\n再加上通脹原因<br />\n無論超支幾多次都好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人睇法 咁係咪政府一直都呃緊廣大市民<br />\n原先話400億內搞掂 但明知要800億既<br />\n等你地班仆街落咗「搭」先<br />\n濕咗個頭再話800億先得<br />\n咁算唔算行騙？<br />\n<br />\n2 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">高鐵只為服務少量市民</span><br />\n有人問佢 我住東鐵線 點解仲要去西九<br />\n佢話你諗下港島同九龍班人<br />\n同學話 東鐵沿線只少佔香港一半（我唔sure)<br />\n田生話 只係重覆話高鐵好快<br />\n早到45分鐘 係港鐵預多咗<br />\n其實30分鐘左右就得<br />\n<br />\n個人睇法 港島人好多都唔撚番大陸<br />\n就算去都唔去廣州<br />\n直接去北京 上海<br />\n搭飛機仲平仲快<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 所有都係外國建築公司錯</span><br />\n高鐵係必需要起<br />\n價錢唔貴 <br />\n之後會好有用<br />\n只係起到有問題<br />\n點都係外判錯<br />\n港鐵冇查清楚 都有少少錯<br />\n政府冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人睇法 收皮<br />\n<br />\n4 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">高鐵唔會回到本</span><br />\n主持問 高鐵賺唔賺得番800億<br />\n田生避咗個問題<br />\n只係識講 港鐵爭取到最大利益<br />\n<br />\n新亞請啲人越嚟越廢<br />\n上次就保蝻義工<br />\n今次就到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706cf8955946a792f6b17d27508ee120a25edccc","tid":827463,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"雖然話好多野大家本身都知<br />\n但今次一個局內人講哂出嚟<br />\n係咪可以拎佢既演講去告政府行騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff4c37c3714706b6e1893c155e64daa638908a4","tid":827463,"uid":13160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"pika<span style=\"color: gold;\">へ　　　　／|<br />\n　　/＼7　　 &ang;＿/<br />\n　 /　│　　 ／　／<br />\n　│　Z ＿,＜　／　　 /ヽ<br />\n　│　　　　　ヽ　　 /　　〉<br />\n　 Y　　　　　　 /　　/<br />\n　ｲ</span>●<span style=\"color: gold;\">　､　</span>●<span style=\"color: gold;\">　　&sub;&sup;〈　　/<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">()</span>　 へ　　<span style=\"color: red;\">()</span>　　|　＼〈<br />\n　　&gt;ｰ ､_　 ィ　 │ ／／<br />\n　 / へ　　 /　ﾉ＜| <span style=\"color: brown;\">＼＼</span><br />\n　 ヽﾉ　　(／　 │<span style=\"color: brown;\">／／</span><br />\n　　7　　　　　　　|／<br />\n　　＞―r￣￣`ｰ―＿6</span>"},{"pid":"4ef1f706284e4d984f5e063926f944522424bf6b","tid":827463,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒"},{"pid":"4d082525f3ee9eb71cd6221a13ee7f503a957377","tid":827463,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ff4c37c3714706b6e1893c155e64daa638908a4","tid":827463,"uid":13160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"pika<span style=\"color: gold;\">へ　　　　／|<br />\n　　/＼7　　 &ang;＿/<br />\n　 /　│　　 ／　／<br />\n　│　Z ＿,＜　／　　 /ヽ<br />\n　│　　　　　ヽ　　 /　　〉<br />\n　 Y　　　　　　 /　　/<br />\n　ｲ</span>●<span style=\"color: gold;\">　､　</span>●<span style=\"color: gold;\">　　&sub;&sup;〈　　/<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">()</span>　 へ　　<span style=\"color: red;\">()</span>　　|　＼〈<br />\n　　&gt;ｰ ､_　 ィ　 │ ／／<br />\n　 / へ　　 /　ﾉ＜| <span style=\"color: brown;\">＼＼</span><br />\n　 ヽﾉ　　(／　 │<span style=\"color: brown;\">／／</span><br />\n　　7　　　　　　　|／<br />\n　　＞―r￣￣`ｰ―＿6</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"咩野事 討論呀"},{"pid":"b069b2ce84c3b8c4767a16f7bf58c9bb1d0aae66","tid":827463,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{